---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Thank You for Your Order">

<div class="container" style="max-width:720px; margin:auto; padding:40px 20px;">

  <h1>Thank you for your order!</h1>

  <p>Your order has been received and your payment has been processed.</p>

  <p>
    I will now confirm availability with the distributor and send you an email update
    shortly with shipping details.
  </p>

  <h2>What happens next</h2>

  <ul>
    <li>I confirm availability with the distributor.</li>
    <li>Your machine will ship via UPS or FedEx.</li>
    <li>I will email you the tracking number as soon as it ships.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>
    If you have any questions in the meantime, feel free to reply to your order email or <a href="/contact">contact us</a>. </p>    <p style="margin-top:30px;">Thank you for supporting Knit it Now.</p>
  </div>
</Layout>